<br>
Problem solved.  I think its a good thing that guilds are willing to hold onto epic items to help their members along and I'd be highly disappointed to have an item that my guild members needed lost too some random stray who tagged along for the ride.<br>
<br>
I've had it done and seen it done in other cases and never cared for it.  I complained when my guild let it happen and I kept my mouth shut when I tagged along for anothers raid.  If I'm going to go too anothers raid, I'm going to follow their rules.  If I dont care for their rules, I wont go on their raids.<br>
<br>
Not that hard to figure out.  Dont want your guild holding items your guild will need, then you need to discuss it with your guild leadership, or find another guild that follows more strictly to what you desire.<br>
